Date: Sat, 29 Nov 2025 15:45:21 +0800
Subject: [PATCH 58/64] [][kernel-6.6/kernel-6.12][mt7988][eth][Update AN8831X
 10G PHY driver to 1.9.1]

[Description]
Update AN8831X 10G PHY driver to 1.9.1.

Changes from Firmware Version 1.9.0:
[firmware]
1. 10G performance is optimized for unstandard RJ45 with WIFI filter.
2. 100meter 10G performance is improved for setup of serial resistor.
   on MDI trace.
3. auto crossover in force 100M mode / parallel detection issue is
   fixed.
[driver]
1. fast/slow mdc is set before and after loading firmware.

[Release-log]
N/A

